== Career highlights ==
=== Tests ===
Test Debut: vs Pakistan, [[Bulawayo]], 2002-2003<br>
Latest Test: vs [[Sri Lankan cricket team|Sri Lanka]], Bulawayo, 2004
*Vermeulen's best Test batting score of 118 was made against [[West Indian cricket team|West Indies]], Bulawayo, 2003-2004

=== One-Day Internationals ===
ODI Debut: vs Sri Lanka, [[Sharjah (city)|Sharjah]], [[2000]]-[[2001]]<br>
Latest ODI: vs [[English cricket team|England]], Bulawayo, 2004-[[2005]]
*Vermeulen's best ODI batting score of 79 was made against Pakistan, Harare, 2002-2003

